      "content": "That's a good start, really sets the mood. I want to zoom in a bit more on the people in that area to make the threat feel more specific. Can you describe a few of the groups or types of people who hang out there? Like, what do they look like, what are they wearing, and what kind of energy do they give off that makes someone feel like they shouldn't be there?",
